<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <h1>Welcome to {{tenantName}}</h1>
  <p>Hello,</p>
  <p>You have been invited by {{invitedBy}} to join {{tenantName}}.</p>
  <p>To accept this invitation, please click the button below:</p>
  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
    <a href="{{invitationUrl}}" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">
      Accept Invitation
    </a>
  </div>
  <p>This invitation will expire on {{expiresAt}}.</p>
  <p>If you did not expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
  <p>Best regards,<br>The {{tenantName}} Team</p>
</div>
